{"tid":1367893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要] 致 727 遊行申請者  唔可以忘記四大原則","createTime":"2019-07-26T11:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T12:19:32.000Z","uid":89160,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d670e6436eae92da425bfbb3cb65b8478ec876f2","tid":1367893,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"致 727 遊行申請者：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>首先，我都認為元朗風險較高，應該以「被動式」勇武為主，即係被打就還手。</strong>不過建議還建議，五大訴求之外，<strong><ins>四大原則</ins></strong>必須貫徹：<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不割席  不分化  不篤魁  兄弟爬山</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n我知你好驚，但唔係用「預先割席」方法解決。遇到「勇武行為」，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">你可以選擇以安全為由，立即解散遊行</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><ins>更重要係，我請你同大家相信勇武派。</ins>我唔係勇武派，但我一直有眼見，<ins>勇武派大體上係進退有度，和平勇武兩者分歧者並不致命</ins>，大家合作已經成個月，<ins>請你唔好先假設「勇武派會失控」</ins>，唔好畀你既恐懼變成大台，變成破壞合作既原因。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家要明白，<strong><ins>已經不存在一個 100% risk free 既集會，無勇武派在場都可以打你，勇武派唔係風險</ins></strong>，風險全在黑社會同政權本身！</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>請你、大家記得初心！</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n聽日會去 shopping 既人 上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HqW52VD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqW52VD.jpg&h=917b0a2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0890f68965672b3bc945c54ade0ea6a6aa84e216","tid":1367893,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:19:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">已經不存在一個 100% risk free 既集會，無勇武派在場都可以打你，勇武派唔係風險</span></strong>"},{"pid":"d3a7111f8e7320505488bffd5bab1e9db1f1aec3","tid":1367893,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:20:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1141b87d30b4c838e6a66690b049e9e3f04b7110","tid":1367893,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T